            "notes": "Models doped fluorite CeO2 as a substitutional solid solution (dopants replace Ce sites) using a CeO2(111) slab. Calculates CO adsorption on clean and vacancy-containing surfaces and surface oxygen vacancy formation energy as low-cost descriptors for CO binding (proxy for ΔH_CO) and reducibility/oxygen mobility (proxy for MvK redox tendency). Uses multiple random dopant configurations (n_configs) to approximate disorder; results can be averaged across seeds/configs."
        },
